Searcher - Interface in adp.elevation.jar
Interface for an object that is capable of running a search for areas of relative flatness in a raster containing elevation data by trying some number of positions in turn.
Searcher.SearchCancelledException - Exception in adp.elevation.jar
An exception class that should be thrown by the Searcher.runSearch(SearchListener) method if another thread invokes Searcher.cancel().
Searcher.SearchListener - Interface in adp.elevation.jar
Interface for objects interested in observing the progress and results of an Searcher object.
